## Quick Verdict

**The Hypervolt Home 3 Pro is the most complete home EV charger on the UK market in 2026.** It combines award-winning design, robust solar integration, smart tariff support, and premium build quality into a single package. It's pricier than rivals like the [Ohme Home Pro](/reviews/ohme-home-pro-review/), but for solar panel owners or anyone who wants the best-looking charger with no compromises, it's exceptionally hard to beat.

**Pros:**
- Stunning design with customisable LED light ring and three colour options
- Three solar charging modes built-in — no extra hardware needed
- Compatible with Intelligent Octopus Go and OVO Charge Anytime
- IP66 + IK10 — the toughest weather and impact rating in its class
- Excellent app with real-time energy monitoring and cost tracking
- Cable wraps neatly around unit — no separate hook needed
- UK-designed and manufactured
- Swappable outer casing for future colour changes

**Cons:**
- Premium price point (~£1,300 installed) — pricier than most rivals
- LED lights can draw unwanted attention (though easily disabled)
- Alexa integration is limited and reportedly buggy
- Cost tracking gets fiddly with complex off-peak tariff windows
- No untethered/socketed option — tethered only

